title: 766. Super Wild Card Weekend Preview
itunes:title: 766. Super Wild Card Weekend Preview
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a new episode of Move the Sticks. Throughout the show, the guys preview every game on Super Wild Card Weekend. Find out the keys to each game, DJ and Bucky's picks, which players need to step up and more on this special episode.
